 is cast with three consecutive full actions over three consecutive rounds, resolving after the third full action is spent.\n\nINST AoE\neDV: CS+9\n\nPhysical resist/physical soak\nTargets that would take any damge from this ability instead lose 1 LUK, if they cannot lose 1 LUK they instead die.\n\nTargets: 50ft Diameter.\n\nOverloads\n\n2: +1 DV\n2: +10ft diameter", "cp": "50", "affinity": {"red": 0, "green": 0, "blue": 0, "black": 0, "white": 0}}, "Energy Wall": {"category": "Spell", "ability_name": "Energy Wall", "ability_description": "1 point of Armor and Structure rating per hit. Barrier regenerates at start of next turn.", "rules": "SUST\n\nCS/2 * 5ft length, 5ft height. CS*2 health. WIL*2 barrier rating. Wall health replenishes end of round.\nAttacks creatures that enter, or are adjacent at end of round, with Spellcasting for CS+9 DV. Wall cannot be cast overlapping creatures.\n\nOverloads\n\n2: +1 DV\n2: +5ft length\n2: +5ft height\n1: +2 hp\n1: +1 barrier rating\n\n", "cp": "5", "affinity": {"red": 0, "green": 0, "blue": 0, "black": 0, "white": 0}}, "Explosive Runes": {"category": "Spell", "ability_name": "Explosive Runes", "ability_description": "Create an explosive magical trap that triggers upon being read", "rules": "", "cp": "10", "affinity": {"red": 0, "green": 0, "blue": 0, "black": 0, "white": 0}}, "Eye of the Hurricane": {"category": "Spell", "ability_name": "Eye of the Hurricane", "ability_description": "Create a wind effect centered on yourself that knocks others back", "rules": "INST AOE SELF\n5ft radius (from self)\neDV = CS + 9\n\nPhysical Resist\nPhysical Soak\n\n0: no effect\n1: 5ft pushback\n9: prone\neach 2 beyond, +5ft pushback\n\nOverloads:\n\n2: +1 eDV\n3: +5ft radius\n\nMake an opposed check against adjacent targets' Physical Resist using your spellcasting dicepool. On success, they are driven back. Succeed by 3 or more and they are knocked prone. Succeed by 6 or more and they are sent flying.\n", "cp": "5", "affinity": {"red": 0, "gr